ANSWER TECHNOLOG said unconsolidated sales
in April fell 41.02% to NT$252,593,000 from NT$428,242,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  4/2011           4/2010
Sales            252,593          428,242    
YOY%             -41.02%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales           1,088,602        1,302,587   
YOY%             -16.43% 
=================================================================
 